  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/6388d6135ff7568f7de7e225223fb46b.poster.avif?t=1730967931\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/6388d6135ff7568f7de7e225223fb46b.webm?t=1730967931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/6388d6135ff7568f7de7e225223fb46b.mp4?t=1730967931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Innovative Core Mechanics:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique Leap Feeling</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple Operation: Hold/Release the Button at the Right Time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/0fbdba31dade91a8932a232c7275d706.poster.avif?t=1730967931\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/0fbdba31dade91a8932a232c7275d706.webm?t=1730967931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2945740/extras/0fbdba31dade91a8932a232c7275d706.mp4?t=1730967931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Gaming Experience:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accurate Timing Control</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Platform-Jumping Game without \"Platforms\"</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store